.SH NAME
pwrdm_has_hdwr_sar \- test whether powerdomain supports hardware SAR
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" pwrdm_has_hdwr_sar
.BI "(struct powerdomain *pwrdm "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pwrdm" 12
struct powerdomain *
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns 1 if powerdomain \fIpwrdm\fP supports hardware save-and-restore
for some devices, or 0 if it does not.
